<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉smk dạ fwq ạ̉sạmynạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ạsmk dạ fwq ạ̉sạmynạ .. wklạmk nwr lʿynynạ)2
 bnḥbk mhmạ qạsynạ .. yạ yswʿnạ yạ gẖạly ʿlynạ
 1- (ḥbk sạkn jwạnạ .. ạsmk ạ̹nt ạlly ʿṭạnạ)2
 nḥyạ fy ṭạʿẗ wạ̉mạnẗ .. ʿlsẖạn ạ̹rạdtk lynạ
 2- (dy mnạbʿ wbtrwyyhạ .. nbʿ yfyḍ dạymaⁿạ fynạ)2
 mn ạsmk nwr ḥwạlynạ .. wwʿwdk mạlyẗ ạ̹ydynạ
 3- (sẖkraⁿạ mhmạ byjry̱ lnạ .. mjdaⁿạ lyk mhmạ qạblnạ)2
 hnqwl sẖkraⁿạ fy ậlạmnạ .. wtḥwlhạ lkẖyr lynạ
 4- (wktbt bdmk lynạ .. kl ḥyạtnạ wkẖṭạwynạ)2
 yạ yswʿ ạ̹nt mḥlynạ .. mhmạ yqwlwạ fy ạ̉sạmynạ</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1595</hymn_number>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
</song>